{"comments":"IsolationMode Atom — Stacking context isolation control.\n\n## Stacking Contexts\n\nIn compositing, elements are grouped into stacking contexts. Within a\ncontext, elements are z-ordered relative to each other. Creating a new\nstacking context isolates the element's children from the parent context.\n\n## Modes\n\n- **Auto**: Element inherits stacking context behavior from ancestors.\n  May or may not create a new context depending on other properties.\n\n- **Isolate**: Element explicitly creates a new stacking context.\n  Children are isolated from parent context's z-ordering.\n\n## When Isolation Matters\n\nIsolation is required when:\n- Using blend modes (children should blend with each other, not background)\n- Complex z-ordering (prevent children from escaping parent bounds)\n- Compositing groups (treat subtree as single unit for effects)\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Schema.Elevation.IsolationMode as Iso\n\n-- Create isolated container\nblendContainer = Iso.isolate\n\n-- Default behavior\nnormalElement = Iso.auto\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[67,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/IsolationMode.purs","start":[67,3]},"title":"Auto"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[68,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/IsolationMode.purs","start":[68,3]},"title":"Isolate"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","IsolationMode"],"IsolationMode"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[70,52],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/IsolationMode.purs","start":[70,1]},"title":"eqIsolationMode"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","IsolationMode"],"IsolationMode"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[71,54],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/IsolationMode.purs","start":[71,1]},"title":"ordIsolationMode"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Generic","Rep"],"Generic"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","IsolationMode"],"IsolationMode"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":null,"tag":"TypeWildcard"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[72,64],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/IsolationMode.purs","start":[72,1]},"title":"genericIsolationMode"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","IsolationMode"],"IsolationMode"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[76,27],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/IsolationMode.purs","start":[74,1]},"title":"showIsolationMode"}],"comments":"Stacking context isolation mode\n\nControls whether an element creates a new stacking context.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"data","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[68,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/IsolationMode.purs","start":[66,1]},"title":"IsolationMode"},{"children":[],"comments":"Auto isolation (inherit from ancestors)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","IsolationMod